
Create React Native project using Expo 
 
    expo init AwesomeProject

Dependencies used in the project

React Navigation
    npm install --save react-navigation
    npm install --save react-navigation-stack

React screen handling 
    npm install --save @react-native-community/masked-view
    npm install --save react-native-safe-area-view 
    npm install --save react-native-safe-area-context

Linking navigation
    react-native link @react-native-community/masked-view
    react-native link react-native-safe-area-context

ToastAndroid 
    npm install react-native-toast-android --save

ImageLoading Placeholder
    npm i --save react-native-image-placeholder

Internet handling
    npm install @react-native-community/netinfo --save
